description: The young woman, who can be identified only as 'A', lacked the ability to make decisions for herself and was put into a care home in 2019 because of her mother's negative influence.

title: Husband kills wife, slits his own throat in front of their kids in horrific murder-suicide
description: Officials say Oscar Mercado Salazar, 31, stabbed his wife, Byanca Cruz Tovar, 26, in front of her three children Monday night in Deltona, Florida before slitting his own throat.

title: Earthquake strikes Victoria as thousands of homes are wrecked by devastating floods
description: The 3.4 magnitude earthquake was recorded in Mansfield, a small town in Victoria's northeast, just after 9am on Wednesday with residents reporting hearing a 'loud boom' and the ground 'shaking'.
